channel.title: RSC Pictures Thread [56k'ers, beware]
channel.description:
I couldn't find a topic like this with search and I thought it would be fun to recall some memories. Post your (random) pictures of the good ol' RuneScape 1.
Pics from a friend of mine who "fixed" AutoRune :P [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img20.imageshack.us/img20/7813/andwhatthecrapisthissk8.jpg[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img20.imageshack.us/img20/588/holycrapoe1.jpg[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img20.imageshack.us/img20/4153/lolreportabuseeb5.jpg[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img58.imageshack.us/img58/6233/mo3jpgne6.jpg[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img247.imageshack.us/img247/8793/omkav1.jpg[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img236.imageshack.us/img236/1251/teleportingtoalkharidpj7.jpg[/img][/URL]
My staker/king of wilderness called pr4y3r k1ng (no, I was the second owner) [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img68.imageshack.us/img68/910/76defap0.png[/img][/URL]
My ranger called Rangeh Pls (I autoed him myself with AR) [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img516.imageshack.us/img516/5411/myynnisli0.png[/img][/URL]
RuneBot 185 (private, updated by evilPat in February 2004) [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img165.imageshack.us/img165/4053/rb185uk5.png[/img][/URL]
Pictures off The Engine. TE was made in Delphi by my friend, Cy4n-. It communicated with my java bot. The project was never really finished. If you're interested in how TE worked, check out [url=http://www.uploadit.biz/download.php?filename=manual24487.htm]the manual.[/url] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img62.imageshack.us/img62/7212/if1javaes3.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img152.imageshack.us/img152/9614/if1textrm4.png[/img][/URL]
A staking bot by Cy4n-: [img]http://www.uploadit.biz/uploads/images/heikkikuva119213.png[/img]
All the chars I was sharing with my friend: [img]http://www.uploadit.biz/uploads/images/ukkoi32772.jpg[/img]
My staking loot: [img]http://www.uploadit.biz/uploads/images/ihaniisisti78743.jpg[/img]
Note for retarded flamers: I do realise that there is really no point in this thread.
